## Tujuan

Implementasi efek bloom (glow di sekitar highlight) dan halation (glow berwarna reddish khas film analog) menggunakan multi-pass FBO rendering. Ini adalah efek paling kompleks di Phase 5 karena membutuhkan multiple render passes dengan Framebuffer Objects.

Baca **docs/deep-research-report.md** (Part 5 – Bloom/Halation: 'extract bright areas (threshold filter), blur them (Gaussian blur on downsampled FBO), additively blend back. Perform blur at lower resolution (half or quarter size), use separable blur') dan **docs/rana_prd.md** (Phase 5 Task 5: 'bloom/halation ringan', note: 'Halation dan bloom lebih sulit karena multi-pass rendering') sebelum implementasi.

## Arsitektur Multi-Pass (3 Pass)

### Pass 1 — Bright-Pass Filter
- Threshold: hanya pixel dengan luminance > threshold yang diloloskan
- Render ke FBO di 1/4 resolusi (quarter-res FBO) untuk efisiensi
```glsl
// Bright pass shader
float luma = dot(color.rgb, vec3(0.299, 0.587, 0.114));
vec3 brightResult = max(color.rgb - vec3(uBloomThreshold), 0.0) / (1.0 - uBloomThreshold);
```

### Pass 2 — Gaussian Blur (2-sub-pass separable)
- Horizontal blur di quarter-res FBO
- Vertical blur di quarter-res FBO
- Separable 1D Gaussian jauh lebih efisien dari 2D Gaussian
```glsl
// 9-tap Gaussian kernel (separable)
const float weights[5] = float[](0.2270, 0.1945, 0.1216, 0.0540, 0.0162);
```

### Pass 3 — Additive Composite
- Upsample blurred result kembali ke full resolution
- Additive blend ke frame utama
- Halation: tint bloom dengan warna reddish-orange sebelum blend

```glsl
vec3 bloomColor = texture2D(uBloomTexture, uv).rgb;
if (uHalationIntensity > 0.0) {
    bloomColor *= mix(vec3(1.0), vec3(1.0, 0.35, 0.15), uHalationIntensity);
}
color.rgb += bloomColor * uBloomIntensity;
```

